8ConnectionGeometry::ConnectionGeometry()
9 : _in(0, 0), _out(0, 0)
10 //, _animationPhase(0)

15QPointF const &ConnectionGeometry::getEndPoint(PortType portType) const
16{
17 Q_ASSERT(portType != PortType::None);
18 return (portType == PortType::Out ? _out : _in);
19}
20void ConnectionGeometry::setEndPoint(PortType portType, QPointF const &point)
21{
22 switch (portType)
23 {
24 case PortType::Out: _out = point; break;
25 case PortType::In: _in = point; break;
26 default: break;
27 }
28}
29void ConnectionGeometry::moveEndPoint(PortType portType, QPointF const &offset)
30{
31 switch (portType)
32 {
33 case PortType::Out: _out += offset; break;
34 case PortType::In: _in += offset; break;
35 default: break;
36 }
37}
38QRectF ConnectionGeometry::boundingRect() const
39{
40 auto points = pointsC1C2();
41 QRectF basicRect = QRectF(_out, _in).normalized();
42 QRectF c1c2Rect = QRectF(points.first, points.second).normalized();
43 auto const &connectionStyle = StyleCollection::connectionStyle();
44 float const diam = connectionStyle.pointDiameter();
45 QRectF commonRect = basicRect.united(c1c2Rect);
46 QPointF const cornerOffset(diam, diam);
47 commonRect.setTopLeft(commonRect.topLeft() - cornerOffset);
48 commonRect.setBottomRight(commonRect.bottomRight() + 2 * cornerOffset);
49 return commonRect;
50}
51std::pair<QPointF, QPointF> ConnectionGeometry::pointsC1C2() const
52{
53 const double defaultOffset = 200;
54 double xDistance = _in.x() - _out.x();
55 double horizontalOffset = qMin(defaultOffset, std::abs(xDistance));
56 double verticalOffset = 0;
57 double ratioX = 0.5;
58 if (xDistance <= 0)
59 {
60 double yDistance = _in.y() - _out.y() + 20;
61 double vector = yDistance < 0 ? -1.0 : 1.0;
62 verticalOffset = qMin(defaultOffset, std::abs(yDistance)) * vector;
63 ratioX = 1.0;
64 }
65 horizontalOffset *= ratioX;
66 QPointF c1(_out.x() + horizontalOffset, _out.y() + verticalOffset);
67 QPointF c2(_in.x() - horizontalOffset, _in.y() - verticalOffset);
68 return std::make_pair(c1, c2);
69}
